Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nova那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只剩Target 1健在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但核心已经半损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最后了 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
