Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ereinbar组合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 都还没洗礼过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍井和也能做到这事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 攻破它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认Target 1活动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他去接触 果然没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我见到苍井和叶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个禁止接触之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想参加Chevalier的预备军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为潘多拉的自己该怎么活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...你当小说家的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个也绝对要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为约定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 去探望嘉涅莎学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 和也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨提拉学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来探病?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底吹什么风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是下雪也要怪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过后到我房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说禁止接触之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前她可不会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和也这时候来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 萨提拉学姊叫我到她房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 得穿点衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨提莱莎 和也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨提拉学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想穿成这样诱惑和也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太不知廉耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更加不知廉耻哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣痕对我们人类来说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是把双刃剑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能培养出更强力的潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 苍井源吾博士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切 从此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了
